---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | SWE AI News">
	<section class="max-w-2xl mt-8">
		<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
			<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
			About the Project
		</h2>
		
		<div class="bg-neutral-900/40 border border-neutral-800/60 rounded-xl p-8">
			<p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
				<strong>SWE AI News</strong> is a curated intelligence aggregator designed specifically for software engineers. In an era where artificial intelligence is fundamentally transforming the way we build, ship, and maintain code, staying updated is no longer optional—it's critical infrastructure for your career.
			</p>
			
			<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-3 mt-8">Our Mission</h3>
			<p class="text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed mb-6 text-sm md:text-base">
				The objective is to parse the noise. We aggregate the most relevant releases, trends, and tools—from autonomous coding agents like Claude Code to foundational framework updates—and distill them into high-signal summaries.
			</p>

			<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-white mb-4 mt-8">Technology Stack</h3>
			<ul class="list-none text-neutral-400 space-y-3 font-mono text-sm bg-black/20 p-4 rounded-lg border border-neutral-800/50">
				<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500"></span> Built with <strong class="text-blue-400">Astro</strong></li>
				<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500"></span> Styled with <strong class="text-blue-400">Tailwind CSS</strong></li>
				<li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-500"></span> Deployed statically for performance</li>
			</ul>
            
			<p class="text-neutral-500 text-xs mt-8 font-mono border-t border-neutral-800/60 pt-6">
				Open source and proudly maintained.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>
